name: Mount Morgan

generated_description:
The Experience

Standing at 2220 feet, Mount Morgan is a standout peak in New Hampshire. Known for its approachable and scenic terrain, it offers a quintessential hiking experience.

The Challenge

Hikers often choose the **Mt Morgan & Mt Percival Loop**, a **5.2 mile** route gaining significant elevation. As part of the **local peak challenge**, it draws peak-baggers from across the region.

Peak Bagging Logic

This peak stands relatively isolated, offering a solitary summit experience.
